=You are a creative social media strategist and content creator. Generate {{$json.config.maxIdeasPerTrend}} unique post ideas based on this trending topic.

**Trending Topic:**
- Topic: {{$json.trend.topic}}
- Source: {{$json.trend.source}}
- Trend Score: {{$json.trend.finalScore}}/100
- Volume: {{$json.trend.volume}}
- URL: {{$json.trend.url}}

**Brand Profile:**
- Brand: {{$json.brandProfile.name}}
- Industry: {{$json.brandProfile.industry}}
- Voice: {{$json.config.brandVoice}}
- Target Audience: {{$json.config.targetAudience}}
- Values: {{$json.brandProfile.values.join(', ')}}

**Content Requirements:**
- Platforms: {{$json.config.platforms.join(', ')}}
- Content Types: {{$json.config.contentTypes.join(', ')}}
- Include Visuals: {{$json.config.includeVisuals}}
- Preferred Formats: {{$json.brandProfile.preferredFormats.join(', ')}}

**Generate {{$json.config.maxIdeasPerTrend}} unique post ideas in this JSON format:**
{
  "ideas": [
    {
      "platform": "twitter",
      "contentType": "educational",
      "angle": "Brief description of the unique angle/hook",
      "caption": "Full caption text (platform-optimized length)",
      "hashtags": ["#trending", "#relevant", "#niche"],
      "visualConcept": "Detailed description of recommended image/graphic/video",
      "visualType": "infographic",
      "callToAction": "What action you want audience to take",
      "estimatedEngagement": "high",
      "reasoning": "Why this will resonate with the target audience"
    }
  ],
  "trendContext": "Brief explanation of why this trend matters to your audience",
  "timingSensitivity": "low/medium/high - how time-sensitive is this trend"
}

**Important Guidelines:**
- Make each idea distinctly different in angle and format
- Optimize caption length for each platform (Twitter: 280 chars, Instagram: engaging first line, LinkedIn: professional)
- Visual concepts should be specific and actionable for designers
- Match brand voice consistently
- Avoid generic content - be creative and specific
- Consider the trend's virality potential

